23. And lastly, if she would gull
thee with that specious and muchaffected Title of Holy Church; tell her that the Spirit of Truth in the Divine Oracles, let her commend her self as much as she pleases, gives no such Character of her, but quite contrary, declaring the See of Rome to be the Apoc. 2. 13. Seat of Satan, and their Church Apoc. 3. 9. his Synagogue; the Pope and his Clergy to be Apoc. 2. 13, 14. Balaam the son of Bozor, who loved the wages of unrighteousnesse, and who was the Murtherer of Christ's faithfull Martyr Antipas; to be that Apoc. 2. 20. Woman Jezebel who calls her self a Prophetesse, but was indeed a Sorceresse, and a murtherer of the true Prophets of the Lord; to be also that Apoc. 19. 20. false Prophet, that is to be taken alive, and cast into the lake of fire and brimstone; to be that Apoc. 11. 8. great City that spiritually is called Sodom and AEgypt, where our Lord was crucified; to be Apoc. 13. 11. the Beast that has the horns of a Lamb, but the voice of the Dragon, decreeing Idolatries and cruel Persecutions against God's people;
to be that Apoc. 17. Babylon the great, the Mother of Harlots and Abominations of the Earth; the Woman on the seven Hills, that is drunk with the bloud of the Saints and with the bloud of the Martyrs of Jesus; and, lastly, to be that 2 Thess. 2. Man of Sin, that notorious Antichrist, that opposeth and exalteth himself above all that is called God or is worshipped, whose coming is with all deceivableness of unrighteousnesse in them that perish, because they receive not the love of the truth that they may be saved. For which cause God sends them strong delusion, that they believe a lie. That they all might be damned that believe not the truth, but have pleasure in unrighteousnesse. As well 〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉 , as 〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉 , as well all they that love the Romish Lies and Impostures, as all they that invent them, are here plainly declared in the state of Damnation.
